							<h5><a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/03/a-belated-farewell-to-a-pioneering-polar-bear-researcher/" title="Read: A Belated Farewell to a Pioneering Polar Bear Researcher">A Belated Farewell to a Pioneering Polar Bear Researcher</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
