				<a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/11/30/teds-science-curator-sees-hope-in-the-anthropocene/"><img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2016/11/29/blogs/dotunnatural/dotunnatural-thumbStandard.jpg" width="50" height="50" /></a>
